meta.@content: HAnim Specification reference example providing full coverage (and no illustrated visibility) of all specified HAnim constructs, also suitable for re-use as an authoring template.
move relevant HAnimSite/Viewpoint pairs into skeleton at appropriate locations
insert MetadataInteger nodes indicating LOA for each Joint and Segment
Norman Badler et al., ANTHROPOMETRY FOR COMPUTER GRAPHICS HUMAN FIGURES, University of Pennsylvania, 1989.
HAnim Specification Table 4.4 - Face Joint object names, https://www.web3d.org/files/specifications/19774/V1.0/HAnim/concepts.html#FaceJointObjectNames
